#### Description

This dashboard offers comprehensive insights into DHCP lease activity within the Infoblox environment. It provides visibility into event volume, severity distribution, protocol usage, and operational patterns over time. The dashboard also highlights key attributes such as host information, MAC and IP addresses, subnets, and fingerprint data, enabling users to detect unusual behaviors or trends. By presenting both high-level summaries and detailed event data, this dashboard supports monitoring, troubleshooting, and auditing efforts across DHCP-related network activity.
